name: Firewall eXceed Dragon
desc:
2+ Level 4 monsters
This Xyz Summoned card gains ATK equal to the total Link Rating of the Link Monsters linked to it x 500. You can detach 2 materials from this card, then target 1 Link-4 Cyberse Link Monster in your GY; Special Summon it to your field so it points to this card, also for the rest of this turn, you cannot Special Summon monsters, nor attack directly.
